-So that's why.
-Ginger on my mind.

19
00:00:52,852 --> 00:00:53,887
-Ginger ramen.
-Ginger ramen.

20
00:00:53,953 --> 00:00:56,289
-I love ginger.
-I see.

21
00:00:56,356 --> 00:00:57,524
