but garlic is the main ingredient.

25
00:01:07,367 --> 00:01:10,837
I can't forget the ginger ramen

26
00:01:10,904 --> 00:01:12,639
here in Asahikawa.

27
00:01:12,705 --> 00:01:13,740
-Really?
-Yes.

28
